### **2. main_APILatencyReporter**  
**Description:**  
A monitoring script that pings endpoints and reports response times and HTTP status codes.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APILatencyReporter - Endpoint Health Tracker

APILatencyReporter allows developers to test response speed and availability of any set of HTTP endpoints.

## Features
- Tracks uptime and latency  
- Prints response summaries  
- Optional output to CSV  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_APILatencyReporter.git
cd main_APILatencyReporter
python monitor.py
